---
layout: base.njk
title: Contact
description: Get in touch with Paws Beyond Odds — questions, stories, or brand partnerships.
pageClass: contact
---

<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-inner">
    <div class="eyebrow">Get in touch</div>
    <h1>Contact <em>Us</em></h1>
    <p>Whether you have a question about your cat, a story to share, or you're a brand interested in partnering — this is the place.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="contact-section">
  <div class="contact-inner">

    <div class="contact-reasons">
      <div class="reason-card">
        <div class="reason-icon">💬</div>
        <h3>Questions about your cat</h3>
        <p>We're not vets, and we can't give medical advice — but we can share what we've learned, point you to the right section of the site, or just listen. You're not alone in this.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="reason-card">
        <div class="reason-icon">📖</div>
        <h3>Share your story</h3>
        <p>If your cat's experience — or your experience as their advocate — could help other owners, we'd love to hear it. Community knowledge is part of what makes this resource better.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="reason-card">
        <div class="reason-icon">🤝</div>
        <h3>Brand partnerships</h3>
        <p>We work with brands whose products genuinely help cat owners managing chronic illness. We're selective, we disclose everything, and we only promote what we'd recommend anyway. See the <a href="{{ '/promotions/' | url }}">deals page</a> for how we approach this.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-form-wrap">
      <h2>Send a message</h2>

      <!--
        FORMSPREE SETUP:
        1. Sign up at formspree.io
        2. Create a new form
        3. Replace YOUR_FORM_ID below with your actual form ID
        e.g. action="https://formspree.io/f/abcdefgh"
      -->
      <form
        action="https://formspree.io/f/YOUR_FORM_ID"
        method="POST"
        class="contact-form"
      >
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="name">Your name</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="What should we call you?" required>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Email address</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="So we can reply" required>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="reason">Reason for getting in touch</label>
          <select id="reason" name="reason">
            <option value="">Select one...</option>
            <option value="cat-question">Question about my cat</option>
            <option value="share-story">Sharing my story</option>
            <option value="partnership">Brand partnership inquiry</option>
            <option value="site-feedback">Site feedback or correction</option>
            <option value="other">Something else</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="message">Message</label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="6" placeholder="Tell us what's on your mind..." required></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group form-footer">
          <p class="form-note">We read every message. Response time is typically 2–5 days. For urgent cat health situations, please contact your vet or an emergency animal hospital.</p>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send Message →</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
.contact-section { padding: 64px 32px; }
